<h2 class="bold font-l">Seven Mortal Sins</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The Seven Mortal Sins are seven demon lords who make up the highest authority in Hell, each of them representing a sin that causes damnation in humanity. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DemonLordsAndArchdevils" class='trope-example-link'>Demon Lords and Archdevils</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="lou3bt" data-video-descrip="As the Demon Lord of Vanity, Belial embodies the very definition of her sin to a tee." data-video-title="Belial" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/lou3bt_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/lou3bt.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/Narcissist" data-video-tropename="Narcissist" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Anime/SevenMortalSins" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/lou3bt.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Belial</span></p>
</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
